n' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>رِجۡسٞ</a> </div><div><a data-content='لعنٌ وطردٌ أو سُخط' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>وَغَضَبٌۖ</a></div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>أَتُجَٰدِلُونَنِي</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> فِيٓ أَسۡمَآءٖ سَمَّيۡتُمُوهَآ أَنتُمۡ </div><div>وَءَابَآؤُكُم</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>مَّا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> نَزَّلَ ٱللَّهُ بِهَا مِن سُلۡطَٰنٖۚ فَٱنتَظِرُوٓاْ إِنِّي مَعَكُم </div><div>مِّنَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱلۡمُنتَظِرِينَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٧١ فَأَنجَيۡنَٰهُ وَٱلَّذِينَ مَعَهُۥ بِرَحۡمَةٖ </div><div>مِّنَّا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div><a data-content='أهلكنا آخر.. المراد الجميع' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>وَقَطَعۡنَا دَابِرَ</a> ٱلَّذِينَ كَذَّبُواْ بِ‍َٔايَٰتِنَاۖ وَمَا كَانُواْ مُؤۡمِنِينَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'></div><div>مُؤۡمِنِينَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>٧٢</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَإِلَىٰ ثَمُودَ أَخَاهُمۡ صَٰلِحٗاۚ قَالَ يَٰقَوۡمِ ٱعۡبُدُواْ </div><div>ٱللَّهَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>مَا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> لَكُم مِّنۡ إِلَٰهٍ غَيۡرُهُۥۖ قَدۡ جَآءَتۡكُم بَيِّنَةٞ مِّن </div><div>رَّبِّكُمۡۖ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>هَٰذِهِۦ</div><div style=